tent/notification.html" class="dropdown-item"><small class="text-muted">Lorem ipsum (12/25/2017)</small><br><div>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet...</div></a><div class="dropdown-divider"></div><a href="/docs/pages/content/notifications.html" class="dropdown-item dropdown-link">See all notifications</a></div></li></ul></nav><nav><ol class="breadcrumb mb-0"><li class="breadcrumb-item">Chat</li></ol></nav></div><div class="content-body"><div class="chat"><div class="chat-messages"><div class="container"><p class="text-center"><small class="text-muted">March 23, 2018</small></p><div class="message-sent"><svg class="chat-avatar"><use href="/docs/assets/img/faces.svg#john"/></svg><p>Hello, there... I need some help!<br><small>8:52 AM</small></p></div><p class="text-center"><small class="text-muted">Jane Doe joined the chat</small></p><div class="message-reply"><svg class="chat-avatar"><use href="/docs/assets/img/faces.svg#jane"/></svg><p>Hi, John. I'm happy to help. What can I do for you today?<br><small>8:54 AM</small></p></div><div class="message-sent"><svg class="chat-avatar"><use href="/docs/assets/img/faces.svg#john"/></svg><p>I can't seem to pull up my order. Can you help me?<br><small>9:02 AM</small></p></div><div class="message-reply"><svg class="chat-avatar"><use href="/docs/assets/img/faces.svg#jane"/></svg><p>Absolutely. You can find the status of, and trak, your order here: www.app.com/orders<br><small>9:03 AM</small></p></div><div class="message-sent"><svg class="chat-avatar"><use href="/docs/assets/img/faces.svg#john"/></svg><p>Works great! Thank you!<br><small>9:07 AM</small></p></div><div class="message-reply"><svg class="chat-avatar"><use href="/docs/assets/img/faces.svg#jane"/></svg><p>I'm glad you made it! :)<br><small>9:08 AM</small></p></div><div class="message-reply"><svg class="chat-avatar"><use href="/docs/assets/img/faces.svg#jane"/></svg><p>Please let me know if you have any more questions.<br><small>9:08 AM</small></p></div><p class="text-center"><small class="text-danger">Ending conversation since you've been inactive too long.</small></p><div class="message-reply"><svg class="chat-avatar"><use href="/docs/assets/img/faces.svg#bot"/></svg><p>Do you want to see the chat source code? <a href="#css-setup" data-toggle="collapse">Click here and take a look.</a><br><small>9:10 AM</small></p></div><div class="source-code"><div id="css-setup" class="collapse"><pre><code class="html">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;chat&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;chat-messages&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;container&quot;&gt;
      &lt;p class&#x3D;&quot;text-center&quot;&gt;
        &lt;small class&#x3D;&quot;text-muted&quot;&gt;March 23, 2018&lt;/small&gt;
      &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;message-sent&quot;&gt;
        &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;john-doe.png&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;chat-avatar&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
          Hello, there... I need some help!
          &lt;br&gt;&lt;small&gt;8:52 AM&lt;/small&gt;
        &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;p class&#x3D;&quot;text-center&quot;&gt;
        &lt;small class&#x3D;&quot;text-muted&quot;&gt;Jane Doe joined the chat&lt;/small&gt;
      &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;message-reply&quot;&gt;
        &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;jane-doe.png&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;chat-avatar&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
          Hi, John. I&#x27;m happy to help. What can I do for you today?
          &lt;br&gt;&lt;small&gt;8:54 AM&lt;/small&gt;
        &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;message-sent&quot;&gt;
        &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;john-doe.png&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;chat-avatar&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
          I can&#x27;t seem to pull up my order. Can you help me?
          &lt;br&gt;&lt;small&gt;9:02 AM&lt;/small&gt;
        &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;message-reply&quot;&gt;
        &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;jane-doe.png&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;chat-avatar&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
          Absolutely. You can find the status of, and trak, your order here: www.app.com/orders
          &lt;br&gt;&lt;small&gt;9:03 AM&lt;/small&gt;
        &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;message-sent&quot;&gt;
        &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;john-doe.png&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;chat-avatar&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
          Works great! Thank you!
          &lt;br&gt;&lt;small&gt;9:07 AM&lt;/small&gt;
        &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;message-reply&quot;&gt;
        &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;jane-doe.png&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;chat-avatar&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
          I&#x27;m glad you made it! :)
          &lt;br&gt;&lt;small&gt;9:08 AM&lt;/small&gt;
        &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;message-reply&quot;&gt;
        &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;jane-doe.png&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;chat-avatar&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
          Please let me know if you have any more questions.
          &lt;br&gt;&lt;small&gt;9:08 AM&lt;/small&gt;
        &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;p class&#x3D;&quot;text-center&quot;&gt;
        &lt;small class&#x3D;&quot;text-danger&quot;&gt;Ending conversation since you&#x27;ve been inactive too long.&lt;/small&gt;
      &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;form class&#x3D;&quot;chat-footer&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;input-group&quot;&gt;
      &lt;input type&#x3D;&quot;text&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;form-control&quot; placeholder&#x3D;&quot;Type a message to Jane&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;input-group-append&quot;&gt;
        &lt;button type&#x3D;&quot;submit&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;btn btn-success&quot;&gt;
          &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fa fa-paper-plane&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
        &lt;/button&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/form&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre></div></div></div></div><div class="chat-footer"><div class="input-group"><input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Type a message to Jane"><div class="input-group-append"><button type="button" class="btn btn-success"><i class="fa fa-paper-plane"></i></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/moment.js/2.22.1/moment.min.js"></script><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.12.0/highlight.min.js"></script><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/2.7.3/Chart.bundle.min.js"></script><script src="/dist/admin4b.min.js?v=2.1.0"></script><script src="/docs/assets/js/docs.js"></script></body></html>